    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>THE WAR.</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/05688217ed4d97af81dd15c3f5c41167.poster.avif?t=1769027390\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/05688217ed4d97af81dd15c3f5c41167.webm?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/05688217ed4d97af81dd15c3f5c41167.mp4?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>They're all dead. The Alien Myriad has invaded and they're all dead. Every country has failed and the whole world is now counting you, the last resort, human's last bastion, the Assassin.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You have everything you need, guns and indefinite ammo:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/3943f71ea2d0edf4dfacc469490ab3fc.poster.avif?t=1769027390\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/3943f71ea2d0edf4dfacc469490ab3fc.webm?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/3943f71ea2d0edf4dfacc469490ab3fc.mp4?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Some of the world's <strong>strongest</strong> weapons made by the best of the best lie in your arms.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What's theirs is yours:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/51c327a839ce0f412140befdf758e1ec.poster.avif?t=1769027390\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/51c327a839ce0f412140befdf758e1ec.webm?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/51c327a839ce0f412140befdf758e1ec.mp4?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Find pieces of AlienTech that they left behind and use it to become even <strong>stronger</strong> and upgrade your equipment.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Even their own abilities:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/4209a102ca107f7b09780e7c1b8baf62.poster.avif?t=1769027390\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/4209a102ca107f7b09780e7c1b8baf62.webm?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/4209a102ca107f7b09780e7c1b8baf62.mp4?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Use your AlienTech-Watch to harness their abilities. Collect more of these <strong>Alien</strong> abilities throughout your journey to use <strong>EVERYTHING</strong> against them.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Connected through your mind, the endless mode:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/2ddff3fcb73e2382a0f8eecb46ced7e9.poster.avif?t=1769027390\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/2ddff3fcb73e2382a0f8eecb46ced7e9.webm?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/2ddff3fcb73e2382a0f8eecb46ced7e9.mp4?t=1769027390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Train and upgrade, gain access to endless mode specific upgrades to train and become <strong>powerful</strong> in ways thought <strong>UNIMAGINABLE</strong>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>WHAT WILL YOU DO ASSASSIN? </strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>COWER IN FEAR? OR BECOME NUMB AND ACCEPT YOUR FATE?</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281940/extras/d5769118421af062e198a0e8bbafbd88.avif?t=1769027390\" width=1450 height=1450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I SEE YOU</strong>: WE WILL MEET.</p></li></ul>",
